name: Black "Fresh Air 5" Black/Grey Mask
description:
People tend to look at Jordanheads as if we’re aliens from another planet. They can’t understand how or why we live and breathe Air Jordan sneakers, but if you’re a collector there’s no explanation necessary. When you pick up a pair of crispy Jordans on Saturday morning, you can’t help but bury your nose in the shoe as soon as you get home…and at that moment it’s as if you become one with the shoe. There’s nothing like Fresh Air, right?

Printed on an all-black Men's shirt that fits true to size.

name: Black "Black Cat"
description:
Jordan’s nickname on the court from fellow NBA players was “Black Cat” for his fast reflexes and speed down the court. The Air Jordan 13, designed by Tinker Hatfield, is said to be inspired by a black panther. The circle stitching on the sneakers represents whiskers, the hologram represents the eyes, and the sole has pads like a paw.

Printed on an all-black Men's shirt that fits true to size.
